<body>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="notification is-danger">
        <h1 class="title is-3">Access Restricted</h1>
        <p>This app uses the Spotify API, which restricts access for security and usage policies. You cannot access it
          unless your account is whitelisted by the administrator.</p>
        <p>If you want to use this app independently, you can <strong>host your own version</strong> by following the
          setup instructions provided in the repository.</p>
        <p>Spotify’s API policies require developers to whitelist applications and users to prevent misuse of their
          service. Unfortunately, this means random users cannot access this demo instance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="box">
        <h2 class="title is-4">Options</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access from the administrator to be whitelisted. You can message <strong>wlczak</strong> on
            discord or send an email to <a href="mailto:vlcek-adam@seznam.cz"><strong>vlcek-adam@seznam.cz</strong></a>.
          </li>
          <li>Fork or clone the repository and run your own local or cloud-hosted version.</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <a class="button is-primary" href="https://github.com/wlczak/lylink" target="_blank">View Repository</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>

